OL,3,COxford United win green light for new
OL,4,C16,000-seat stadium
OL,6,FOxford United's plans for a new
OL,7,Fstadium have been given the green
OL,8,Flight by the government.
OL,10,FThe Secretary of State for Housing,
OL,11,FCommunities and Local Government,
OL,12,FSteve Reed, has confirmed he will not
OL,13,Fcall in the application after it was
OL,14,Fgranted planning permission by
OL,15,FCherwell District Council.
OL,17,FThe club wants to build the stadium on
OL,18,Fgreen belt land known as the Triangle
OL,19,Fwhich is close to the Kidlington
OL,20,Froundabout and Oxford Parkway.
