OL,3,COxford United win green light for new
OL,4,C16,000-seat stadium
OL,6,FIt needed to find a new home because
OL,7,Ftheir current agreement to play at the
OL,8,FKassam Stadium in Littlemore was due
OL,9,Fto end in 2026.
OL,11,FAfter being approved by Cherwell
OL,12,FDistrict Council in August, plans were
OL,13,Freferred to the Secretary of State due
OL,14,Fto the size of the proposed
OL,15,Fdevelopment, which includes a 180-
OL,16,Fbedroom hotel, gym and conference
OL,17,Fcentre.
