OL,3,COxford United win green light for new
OL,4,C16,000-seat stadium
OL,6,FGrant Ferguson, Chairman of Oxford
OL,7,FUnited, said: "The government review
OL,8,Fwas conducted after Cherwell District
OL,9,FCouncil's Planning Committee approved
OL,10,Fthe plans on 14 August.
OL,12,F"The Secretary of State's decision to
OL,13,Fnot to call in the planning
OL,14,Fapplication for our 16,000-capacity
OL,15,Fstadium on land north of the city
OL,16,Fmeans the Club can now begin to
OL,17,Fdeliver on its vision.
