OL,3,COxford United win green light for new
OL,4,C16,000-seat stadium
OL,6,F"On behalf of everyone at Oxford
OL,7,FUnited, I would like to thank all of
OL,8,Four supporters, along with the
OL,9,Fincredible project team who have been
OL,10,Finstrumental in getting us to this
OL,11,Fpoint."
OL,13,FCouncillor Susan Brown, Leader of
OL,14,FOxford City Council said: "I'm
OL,15,Fabsolutely delighted that Oxford
OL,16,FUnited's new stadium has been given
OL,17,Fthe green light by the government.
OL,18,FThis is a huge day for Oxford and
OL,19,FOxfordshire.
