OL,4,C16,000-seat stadium
OL,6,F"The 16,000-seater stadium secures the
OL,7,Fclub's future and offers a host of
OL,8,Feconomic and social benefits for the
OL,9,Farea, including new jobs, improved
OL,10,Ftransport connections, and increased
OL,11,Fsupport for grassroots sport."
OL,13,FCommenting on Facebook, Oxford East MP
OL,14,FAnneliese Dodds said: "Sean Woodcock
OL,15,FMP (Banbury) and I are thrilled that
OL,16,FMHCLG are not calling in the planning
OL,17,Fapplication for Oxford United Official
OL,18,F's vital new stadium.
