OL,3,COxford United win green light for new
OL,4,C16,000-seat stadium
OL,6,FIn a statement a spokesperson said:
OL,7,F"FoSB did not expect the proposed
OL,8,Fstadium application to be called in by
OL,9,Fthe Secretary of State because it
OL,10,Fdoesn't meet the criteria and call ins
OL,11,Fare very rare.
OL,13,F"His decision is certainly not an
OL,14,Fendorsement of the proposal, he merely
OL,15,Fthinks it should be decided at a local
OL,16,Flevel.
